	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm pretty new to gameboy homebrewing but I've been playing around with it for awhile made a game or two. But so far I haven't found a good<br />way to make music for it.<br /><br />Been looking around for tools for it, found a couple of people writing about &quot;Lemon Player&quot; but all the links I find to it are dead. Other then that I only found trackers that<br />runs on the gameboy such as LSDJ and Carillon. Haven't had time to look into them all to closely yet, but are you able to export the songs from them to something that is useable?<br /><br />What would you recommend?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
